    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Allied creatures within 15ft that take damage, has the damage they would take reduced by half, and you take damage equal to the damage originally reduced. <br />The damage done is of the same type the allied creature originally took. <br />Additionally, if you and the allied creatures would take damage as the result of the same area of effect, all creatures within 15ft including you, takes half damage from the area of effect.</p>",
